# ElevateHer ML service environment.
#
# The service currently reads NO required environment variables: it listens on
# port 8000 (see Dockerfile / `uvicorn main:app --port 8000`) and allows all CORS
# origins in development (see main.py). The variables below are reserved for future
# hardening and are documented here so the deployment surface is discoverable.
#
# Port the FastAPI service listens on (matches the Dockerfile default).
# PORT=8000
#
# Comma-separated list of allowed CORS origins for production (currently "*").
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5000
